Constructor Detail

Airplane

public Airplane(java.lang.String model,
                java.lang.String manufacturer,
                int firstClassSeats,
                int coachSeats)
Makes an object that represents an airplane.

The airplane data represents the data that is represented by the XML data that is on the database.

Parameters:
model - the model of the airplane, i.e. "A310".
manufacturer - the company that made the airplane, i.e. "Boeing".
firstClassSeats - the number of first class seats on the airplane.
coachSeats - the number of coach seats on the airplane.
See Also:
XMLGetter.getAirplaneXML()
